  <title>Slider</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword>Definition<keyword>Slider</keyword></keyword>
    <keyword>Motion-Part<keyword>Slider</keyword></keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><table styleclass="PopupTable" rowcount="1" colcount="2" style="width:450px;">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:174px;">
          <para styleclass="VariableName-small"><image src="MD-Pop-Kin-Slider.png" scale="100.00%" figurelistinclude="0"><caption><![CDATA[Slider]]></caption></image></para>
        </td>
        <td style="width:266px;">
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box2">Slider</text> - a <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Part</text> that is joined to a <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Part</text> with a <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Slide-Joint" styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Slide-Joint</link><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">&#32;</text><image src="Red-14-1.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image>&#32;</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">Its position defined by a <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Motion-Dimension-FB" styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Motion-Dimension FB</link><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">&#32;</text><image src="Red-14-2.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">It is a <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Part</text> that is <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Part-Kinematically-Defined" styleclass="VariableName-small">kinematically-defined</link></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="SeeAlso-small">See also: <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Rocker" styleclass="Popup Box2">Rocker</link>, <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Dyad">Dyads</link></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
